titleNullable: Temperature and Humidity of Kolkata from 2015-2020
subtitleNullable: 5 years of Temperature and Humidity measurements in Kolkata
descriptionNullable:
### Context

City of Kolkata is known for its unpredictable weather throughout the year. The challenge is to forecast temperature and humidity at a short-term or long-term temporal dependency. 


### Content

Hourly temperature and humidity data of 5 years from 2015 to 2020.

### Inspiration

Its a beginner friendly time series dataset wherein Kagglers could come up with different approaches with some interesting EDA.

### Acknowledgements
The data is collected from - (https://www.worldweatheronline.com/)
